@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "關於我們";
}

<div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-header">
            <h1>關於唐寶寶公益募資平台</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">連結愛心與希望，讓每個夢想都能實現</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="mission-section">
                <h2>我們的使命</h2>
                <p>唐寶寶公益募資平台成立於2021年，是一個專注於為唐氏症兒童及其家庭提供募資支持的公益平台。我們相信每個孩子都應該擁有平等發展的機會，透過群眾的力量，集結社會各界的愛心，為唐寶寶們創造更好的未來。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="values-section">
                <h2>平台特色</h2>
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                        <h3>透明公開</h3>
                        <p>所有募資專案全程透明，定期公布資金使用狀況，讓每位贊助者都能清楚了解善款流向。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <h3>安全可靠</h3>
                        <p>嚴謹的專案審核機制，確保每個募資專案的真實性，保障贊助者的權益。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        <h3>社群支持</h3>
                        <p>建立互助互愛的社群氛圍，讓每個家庭都能感受到社會的溫暖與支持。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-section">
                <h2>平台發展歷程</h2>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="year">2021</div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>平台成立</h3>
                            <p>唐寶寶公益募資平台正式上線，開始為唐氏症家庭提供募資服務。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="year">2022</div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>服務擴展</h3>
                            <p>新增線上募資功能，並建立專案追蹤系統。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="year">2023</div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>社群成長</h3>
                            <p>累計幫助超過100個唐氏症家庭，募資總額突破千萬。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="year">2024</div>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>創新發展</h3>
                            <p>推出專案回饋機制，讓贊助者能更深入了解專案進展。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="impact-section">
                <h2>平台影響力</h2>
                <div class="impact-grid">
                    <div class="impact-item">
                        <div class="impact-number">100+</div>
                        <p>成功募資專案</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-item">
                        <div class="impact-number">10M+</div>
                        <p>募資總額</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-item">
                        <div class="impact-number">5000+</div>
                        <p>贊助者人數</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-item">
                        <div class="impact-number">98%</div>
                        <p>專案成功率</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-section">
                <h2>專業集團</h2>
                <div class="team-grid">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="~/images/team1.jpg" alt="團隊成員">
                        <h3>思考明天午餐吃甚麼</h3>
                        <p>平台營運</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="~/images/team2.jpg" alt="團隊成員">
                        <h3>早上睡覺基金會</h3>
                        <p>媒體、活動邀約</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="~/images/team3.jpg" alt="團隊成員">
                        <h3>不看新聞與時事脫離，看了新聞與事實脫離</h3>
                        <p>相關報導聯繫</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .page-wrapper {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 60px); /* 減去頁尾的高度 */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .about-container {
        flex: 1;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .about-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6A994E 0%, #B5C99A 100%);
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        color: white;
    }

    .about-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .about-header .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .mission-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 15px;
    }

    .mission-section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .mission-section p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #666;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .values-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .values-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .value-item {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .value-item:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .value-item i {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #6A994E;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .value-item h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .value-item p {
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .impact-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        padding: 3rem 0;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 15px;
    }

    .impact-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .impact-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .impact-item {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .impact-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #6A994E;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .impact-item p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .history-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .history-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 2px;
        height: 100%;
        background: #6A994E;
    }

    .timeline-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 2rem 0;
        position: relative;
    }

    .timeline-item .year {
        background: #6A994E;
        color: white;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item .content {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        width: 300px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .timeline-item .content h3 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-item .content p {
        color: #666;
    }

    .team-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .team-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .team-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .team-member {
        text-align: center;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .team-member:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .team-member img {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        border: 4px solid #6A994E;
    }

    .team-member h3 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .team-member p {
        color: #666;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-container {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .about-header {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .mission-section {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .mission-section p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .values-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .impact-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            left: 0;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-left: 2rem;
        }

        .timeline-item .year {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        }

        .timeline-item .content {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .team-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .team-member {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
    }
</style> 